title: THE LUCY SHOW -- Lucy and the Countess ( with Ann Sothern )
description:
The first of several episodes with Ann Sothern as Rosie, a former classmate of Lucy's, who eventually married a count.  Rosie was in 4 episodes late in this season filling in for Vivian Vance as Viv was out of town visiting relatives.

After Lucy moved cross country to Los Angeles at the start of Season 4, Rosie turned up in two more episodes including one I already uploaded
